&lt;p&gt;It had been several hours since the start of our hike, and Junior was visibly tired. We decided to take the bus back to Trieste from here.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It is possible to continue on the trail from the church, and reach the Obelisk, the starting point of our walk. On our list for next time! ðŸ™‚&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This scenic walking trail, the Strada Vicentina (Strada Napoleonica), was the highlight of our visit to Trieste. Junior talks about it excitedly even today!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

